{"tid":2228882,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"川普確診後信心爆棚？ 拜登：再一個月就能叫妻子第一夫人","createTime":"2020-10-04T03:17:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-04T09:23:21.000Z","uid":28765,"like":13,"dislike":473,"uniUserReply":100,"replies":[{"pid":"a94cdd17a4d790bf51d2aca7f2bf88f567542cab","tid":2228882,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T03:17:49.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國總統川普確診武漢肺炎（新型冠狀病毒病，COVID-19），為即將到來的11月總統大選投下震撼彈，代表民主黨參選的拜登（Joe Biden）曾在美東時間2日在推特表示他將成為美國總統，而稍早又推文聲稱再過一個月就能叫妻子吉兒（Jill Biden）「第一夫人」了。<br />\n<br />\n拜登稍早在推特推文中宣稱：「再過一個月我們就能叫拜登夫人『第一夫人』了。」並強調，目前美國正面臨著前所未有的危機。 但是他知道，美國人民有能力克服他們。<br />\n<br />\n.....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3311058\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3311058&d=YLq6vaBnyeHQX05GIPWJdsls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=dc99ab85\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3311058&h=b75bcec2\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3311058</a>"},{"pid":"b88a767d160679de326098770802f95e2b276546","tid":2228882,"uid":274149,"like":723,"dislike":5,"score":718,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T03:23:05.000Z","msg":"拜登一定會好似希拉莉咁，贏到開巷"},{"pid":"3d44dc60c8a2f5376a2b49a61c2043e17e50ca6b","tid":2228882,"uid":229916,"like":127,"dislike":2,"score":125,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T03:24:31.000Z","msg":"贏登，連登全體G 持拜登當選<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96d33d26dc410af9a7a516373757b5e928271616","tid":2228882,"uid":29093,"like":64,"dislike":0,"score":64,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T03:27:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最後的自戀"},{"pid":"3173c3367003b841543a640cb710b3b9465a67ad","tid":2228882,"uid":370148,"like":168,"dislike":1,"sco